        <abstract> 
<p><hi rend="italic">Orchids</hi> is at last sold out. Settles account.</p>  
<p>The <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> [6th ed.] is making good [sales] progress.</p>  
<p><hi rend="italic">Expression</hi> is not selling.</p> 
